Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.51,0:00:04.58,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'll reimburse you for the magic hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.52,0:00:06.43,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.07,0:00:08.33,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was my fault for scaring you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.47,0:00:13.17,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But don't you need it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.37,0:00:15.03,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, to go home and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.60,0:00:20.53,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know we need one. That's why I've already bought another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:23.04,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, there was a special offer going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.13,0:00:25.16,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so I got two.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.59,0:00:26.56,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You really need it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.71,0:00:27.46,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And two of them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.14,0:00:32.90,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I feel like I benefited, so don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.26,0:00:33.94,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Benefited...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.94,0:00:35.96,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.45,0:00:37.30,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.77,0:00:38.89,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.50,0:00:41.43,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.21,0:00:44.43,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, last night, Yamada and Inami-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.46,0:00:47.45,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.08,0:00:52.75,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really think we need to hide the fact that we went to your house last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.23,0:00:55.08,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad for Taneshima-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.47,0:00:55.95,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.68,0:01:00.05,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The stuff about my sisters my past could get out,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.67,0:01:02.70,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so everything about my family is a secret from Senpai.
Comment: 0,0:01:03.33,0:01:03.45,Working - TS,,0000,0000,0000,,[Wilting]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.33,0:01:05.20,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But she looks so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.69,0:01:06.15,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.48,0:01:07.33,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.54,0:01:10.43,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A sad Senpai is fine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.98,0:01:13.00,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean it like that.
Comment: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:17.01,Working - TS,,0000,0000,0000,,[An unexpected night before the match. Taneshima's Repayment.]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.56,0:01:19.08,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Well then, good work everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.52,0:01:22.73,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Huh? You sure are in a hurry today, Katanashi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.01,0:01:24.45,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You're not going home with Inami-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.96,0:01:26.97,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, the soy sauce is on special offer today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.11,0:01:27.84,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Soy sauce?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.15,0:01:28.41,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.24,0:01:32.19,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It may be sold out already since they're about to close.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.96,0:01:34.31,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't want to give up until the very end!
Comment: 0,0:01:35.03,0:01:35.19,Working - TS,,0000,0000,0000,,[Inside the girl's locker room]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.96,0:01:35.77,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.03,0:01:36.20,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.47,0:01:38.91,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost to soy sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.26,0:01:43.81,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She sure is dreamy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.28,0:01:46.70,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Slim, tall, mature-looking,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.05,0:01:51.07,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and, on top of being cute, has a cool ambiance about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.77,0:01:54.53,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Katanashi-kun really is the ultimate woman, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.77,0:01:56.13,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If he wasn't a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.75,0:01:57.41,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really my type, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.77,0:02:01.36,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you're still bringing this up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.86,0:02:03.08,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you into girls or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.98,0:02:06.21,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We already have enough of that with Todoroki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.53,0:02:07.79,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.01,0:02:10.03,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not love, it's a matter of aspiration!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:12.16,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... How to put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.79,0:02:18.03,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,340)}Like tall, busty, slim, and amazing!
Comment: 0,0:02:15.15,0:02:17.15,Working - TS,,0000,0000,0000,,ceheck fade for above
Comment: 0,0:02:17.15,0:02:17.19,Working - TS,,0000,0000,0000,,[Tall, Busty, Slim, Amazing]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.67,0:02:20.65,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to become someone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.28,0:02:23.16,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, you need to become taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.50,0:02:27.20,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I need to grow...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.30,0:02:30.76,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Being tall isn't all it's cracked up to be. You hit your head all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.80,0:02:33.47,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You stand out whether you like it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.91,0:02:34.98,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can reach almost anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.95,0:02:39.93,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll feel out of place at movies or when\Nwatching fireworks, but you can see really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:43.62,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can breathe easier in packed trains\Nbecause you're one head taller than everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.90,0:02:45.61,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're just bragging!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.03,0:02:51.83,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope he'll dress up as sa girl again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:53.15,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt he'll do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.18,0:02:58.68,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, remember Inami-chan could touch Katanashi-kun when he was cross-dressed,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.16,0:03:03.50,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so Inami-chan will be able to get closer to\NKatanashi-kun, and I can receive some of her hot-girl aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.98,0:03:06.50,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone will be happy if Katanashi-kun cross-dresses!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.71,0:03:07.66,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But Takanashi will be miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:09.11,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:12.65,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, cross-dressing won't be happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.34,0:03:17.34,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he keeps things from me because I think about these things.
Comment: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:15.88,Working - TS,,0000,0000,0000,,[Girl's locker room]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:18.41,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.95,0:03:20.28,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he not like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:23.27,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true, Taneshima-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:24.65,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Inami-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.06,0:03:27.93,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,He just doesn't want you finding out about his sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:30.06,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything, he likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,0:03:33.28,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He likes you way more than me.
Comment: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:31.39,Working - TS,,0000,0000,0000,,[He likes you way more than me]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.76,0:03:35.87,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Inami-chan? Your voice is shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:38.35,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're tiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.10,0:03:40.80,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So Inami's probably right about him liking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.91,0:03:43.55,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.17,0:03:48.80,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... Katanashi-kun's student notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.30,0:03:51.91,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,His train pass is in here. He must have dropped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.64,0:03:55.90,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to need it tomorrow. \NI've got to deliver it to his house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:03:58.38,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be all right by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.11,0:04:00.68,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My shift's not over, so I can't give you a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.00,0:04:01.93,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:03.67,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems his house isn't far from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.90,0:04:04.81,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:08.18,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be bad if she meets Kozue-san at his house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:10.10,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm still dressing, so I can't get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.72,0:04:14.79,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Katanashi-kun's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.26,0:04:16.45,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,It's bigger than mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.78,0:04:19.64,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing. Does he have a huge family?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.31,0:04:24.71,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:28.06,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,So tall!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.65,0:04:29.55,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,So tiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.17,0:04:32.38,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Cross-dressed Katanashi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:33.79,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.11,0:04:35.04,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,His sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:38.69,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.73,0:04:44.64,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:47.21,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,She's definitely Katanashi-kun's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:49.81,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this cute little thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:51.46,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, did you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.98,0:04:53.46,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, the train pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.82,0:04:56.15,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, It's Taneshima-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:04:57.55,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.72,0:04:58.54,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:03.03,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,Katanashi's regular customer and\NKatanashi-kun's little sister, Nazuna-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.54,0:05:06.55,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,Given that they all live together like this, it must mean that they're...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:08.36,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Katanashi-kun's family?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.61,0:05:09.68,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Takanashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:13.14,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to get some soy sauce, but I lost my train pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:14.70,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I leave it at work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.53,0:05:17.45,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to go to school tomorrow without my train pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:19.21,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, what a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:21.68,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Senpai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.56,0:05:23.36,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.45,0:05:27.45,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that Nazuna-chan was your really tall little sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:30.31,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but, not only is our regular drunken customer really your older sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:33.00,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you also have another really tall older sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.17,0:05:34.65,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's also one more older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:37.82,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,F-For the time being...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:40.01,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to worship you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:41.71,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not blessed by the gods! {Keeper: TLC, Or is it more of a "worshipping them won't make you taller"-thing? | orig line "We don't have any divine blessings!"}
