Comment: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:43.73,Working - TS,,0000,0000,0000,,[Grow~]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:49.99,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Taneshima-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.92,0:05:52.88,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, Katanashi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.02,0:05:53.78,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Takanashi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:57.88,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know... Kozue-neesan is totally pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.01,0:05:59.31,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:03.93,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried that you'd make fun of me or hate me if you found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:08.61,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't think of anything so mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.99,0:06:11.98,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Katanashi-kun doesn't trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:14.85,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost my confidence as a Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:17.18,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,You had confidence...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:22.70,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, it seems that I hurt Senpai's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.93,0:06:25.20,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I told you it wasn't something you should hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:27.05,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Things got even more complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:29.45,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so tiny in that position.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.48,0:06:35.13,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You just thought that a tiny Senpai was cute, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:36.61,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I didn't think that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:38.90,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.95,0:06:41.65,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.65,0:06:42.55,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:44.93,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be better if you apologized sooner rather than later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.43,0:06:46.43,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:48.67,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I see her like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.31,0:06:51.56,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just get an urge to take her home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.95,0:06:55.13,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are... so many reasons why you shouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.69,0:06:58.45,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Taneshima-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.11,0:07:00.00,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Inami-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.36,0:07:03.91,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that Takanashi-kun treasures you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:06.75,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that he couldn't bring himself to\Ntell you about his embarrasing sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.56,0:07:13.01,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In my case, he said that he didn't even care if I found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.34,0:07:14.48,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Katanashi-kun is so mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:16.04,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel so bad for you, Inami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:18.15,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I meant to soothe her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.39,0:07:22.88,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anyway, he's always thought of you as his precious Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.66,0:07:25.36,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's forgive him, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:27.66,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:29.05,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Inami-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:31.24,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really a great person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:35.30,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Katanashi-kun doesn't even realize that a really great person like you likes him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.12,0:07:38.19,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Katanashi-kun is so mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.21,0:07:38.70,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:41.45,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I pitiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:42.81,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.51,0:07:44.43,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:46.56,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,for keeping secrets from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:51.73,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Katanashi-kun, this has been on my mind for a long time now,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:53.95,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but you don't seem to quite understand how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.99,0:07:56.58,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,Nor how Inami-chan feels...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:07:59.12,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand your feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.64,0:08:00.56,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.19,0:08:03.16,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I understood children's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:05.23,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly what I'm talking about!
Comment: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:05.54,Working - TS,,0000,0000,0000,,[Rage]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:06.45,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl's feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:10.81,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was angry that you didn't trust me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:12.30,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:15.95,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To make up for it, I'll do anything you want me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:17.16,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:20.21,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.70,0:08:22.81,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,She might make me cross-dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.09,0:08:24.68,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.56,0:08:26.91,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,go on a date with Inami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.56,0:08:30.84,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were going to make me cross-dress.
Comment: 0,0:08:28.57,0:08:28.61,Working - TS,,0000,0000,0000,,[Impossible]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:33.33,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to do that, even though I want to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.00,0:08:36.21,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's for you to learn to understand a girl's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.63,0:08:39.46,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And as an token of gratitude for\NInami-chan always taking care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.93,0:08:40.77,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand the feelings part,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.18,0:08:42.78,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but why is the date an expression of gratitude for Inami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:46.55,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I-It'll be a great opportunity to fix her androphobia.
Comment: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:45.67,Working - TS,,0000,0000,0000,,[Impossible]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:48.22,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:49.48,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Souma-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:52.22,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on a date while cross-dressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:54.08,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that with a smile on your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.61,0:08:56.35,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:08:58.22,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have to think about it to know that I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.67,0:09:00.78,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,While it would be nice if her first date was with a guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.21,0:09:03.03,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if, by chance, there was someone\Nthat Inami-san actually started to like,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.33,0:09:05.61,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,wouldn't you want her to be able to go on her first date with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:10.93,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, if you cross-dress, it'll won't count.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.27,0:09:11.98,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Souma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.31,0:09:15.71,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to think that this will be pretty funny.
Comment: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:13.36,Working - TS,,0000,0000,0000,,[Seems fun]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.44,0:09:17.66,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:21.50,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, Inami-san wouldn't get so nervous if she were with a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.92,0:09:22.86,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it, Inami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.93,0:09:27.88,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Taneshima-san, you'll get to see Kotori-chan too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.02,0:09:29.55,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Souma-san, you're amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.63,0:09:30.65,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.77,0:09:31.50,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.58,0:09:37.25,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to cross-dress for someone\NInami-san might fall in love with in the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:41.93,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,But, as a guy, I wouldn't want to get beaten up by my date.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.79,0:09:44.59,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,I should listen to Senpai's request.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.32,0:09:48.31,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,And I do want to know how much\NInami-san's androphobia has improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:50.74,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to cross-dress but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.62,0:09:55.37,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm fine with the date but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.43,0:09:56.76,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to cross dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.78,0:09:58.22,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The date is already decided?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.59,0:10:04.36,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.44,0:10:07.30,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do about the date with Takanashi-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:14.22,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.16,0:10:18.04,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.19,0:10:23.89,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I always like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:26.78,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go on a date like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.34,0:10:29.46,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing back here, Inami-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.26,0:10:33.60,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Taneshima-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:37.22,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Takanashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.68,0:10:39.13,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... somewhat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.96,0:10:40.68,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.42,0:10:43.45,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That one really hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.36,0:10:46.52,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Inami-san is especially dangerous today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.63,0:10:47.40,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.88,0:10:49.91,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is the fifth time today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:50.73,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.62,0:10:54.05,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I can go on a date with her like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.68,0:10:56.08,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, just cross-dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:01.83,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather keep getting hit than cross-dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.65,0:11:06.50,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So the thought of not going on\Nthe date doesn't even occur to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.30,0:11:09.86,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Takanashi-kun is really earnest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.28,0:11:16.53,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:19.93,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Going on a date is impossible after all, Taneshima-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:22.26,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to call this whole thing off.
Comment: 0,0:11:22.87,0:11:22.99,Working - TS,,0000,0000,0000,,[Flash]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.58,0:11:23.98,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tepid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.03,0:11:25.96,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:27.75,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're tepid, Inami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.09,0:11:30.83,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your burning passion to cure your androphobia isn't hot enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.24,0:11:32.73,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:33.81,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:36.16,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never be able to fix it like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:40.03,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Inami-chan, do you plan on hitting\NKatanashi-kun for the rest of your life?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.04,0:11:45.00,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest of my life... Rest of my life....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.02,0:11:46.77,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the part you should be thinking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:49.24,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Inami-chan, you still have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.63,0:11:51.65,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to work hard, fix your androphobia,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.03,0:11:53.76,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and succeed on this date.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.43,0:11:55.29,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Taneshima-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.08,0:11:57.51,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.01,0:11:59.03,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:01.13,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:05.10,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's also a fact that there's not\Na whole lot of time before the date.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.26,0:12:08.50,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to take some drastic measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.86,0:12:09.70,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.36,0:12:10.75,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.25,0:12:11.45,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:12.47,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rope?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.91,0:12:13.44,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Handcuffs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:14.00,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.55,0:12:16.14,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada-san, why do you have those?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:21.20,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahiru-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.16,0:12:24.62,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Prisoner?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.90,0:12:28.52,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mostly as punishment for hitting guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.20,0:12:30.48,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel a little bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:33.93,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but for the time being, I made it so she can't use her hands to hit people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.33,0:12:37.01,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go test it out on the kitchen staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:39.38,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So... can she work without her hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:42.18,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Poplar-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.44,0:12:45.21,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:47.05,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Inami-chan, in her current state, is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:48.06,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:49.55,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to touch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.92,0:12:52.18,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay...
Comment: 0,0:12:52.18,0:12:54.18,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,this line above: time and fix
Comment: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:55.92,Working - TS,,0000,0000,0000,,[Poke]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.28,0:12:59.85,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you poking her with chopsticks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:00.75,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:01.91,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a cooking chopstick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.15,0:13:02.91,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's longer than an ordinary chopstick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.88,0:13:05.65,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you poking her with a cooking chopstick?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.07,0:13:07.28,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we're still too scared to use our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:08.22,Working - TS,,0000,0000,0000,,[Stab]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.75,0:13:11.49,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you poking me as well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.61,0:13:12.47,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.80,0:13:14.99,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't you poke Yamada?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.36,0:13:16.55,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel left out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:18.87,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-what? Uh... Because we don't have any interest?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:21.53,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please poke Yamada too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:22.16,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Taneshima.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.08,0:13:24.51,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Inami falls under Takanashi's jurisdiction, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:26.66,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take her to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.06,0:13:28.35,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The wrong jurisdiction?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:29.13,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.85,0:13:31.23,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a bureaucracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.11,0:13:34.55,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,On a side note, Souma's in charge of Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.61,0:13:34.88,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:38.31,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please poke me! Please poke me!
Comment: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:37.29,Working - Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,make sure timing ^ and v is ok
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:39.31,Working - Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm in charge of bullying you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.83,0:13:41.46,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I don't want you in charge of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:42.53,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:44.58,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The people here are useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.89,0:13:47.24,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You brought her here without asking, so do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:51.78,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we'll have to simulate the actual\Nevent, and have the guy himself cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.09,0:13:59.60,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A date...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.09,0:14:02.38,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Katanashi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:06.45,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you finally did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:08.41,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it a great idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.90,0:14:12.24,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, I've thought of this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.30,0:14:13.13,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,You have?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.57,0:14:15.80,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, try touching her, with your bare hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.15,0:14:18.67,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I thought about it, but if I do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.01,0:14:28.35,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew she'd kick me like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.66,0:14:29.98,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,She powered up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.83,0:14:32.74,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So basically...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.98,0:14:37.00,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After the experiment, we've found\Nthat if we bind her hands, she'll kick instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.59,0:14:39.44,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And, if she can't kick,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.61,0:14:42.05,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,she'd probably headbutt or bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.38,0:14:44.85,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So we're going to have to fix all the possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.56,0:14:47.91,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,Now there are more issues...
Comment: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:46.23,Working - TS,,0000,0000,0000,,[Issues]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.11,0:14:50.90,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just as I thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:53.25,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we should call the date off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.53,0:14:54.05,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:55.40,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Inami-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.11,0:14:59.63,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Because it still didn't work out with me like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.15,0:15:01.34,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we go on a date...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:04.06,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:06.01,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,beat the crap out of Takanashi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.81,0:15:08.30,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I already know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:08.83,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.28,0:15:12.04,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I accepted knowing that would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.53,0:15:15.41,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't have to worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:20.00,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.58,0:15:24.13,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Katanashi-kun is such a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:25.99,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:31.36,Working - TS,,0000,0000,0000,,[And now, the night before the date]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.23,0:15:33.06,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'll be heading out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:37.61,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You two have the day off tomorrow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.98,0:15:38.26,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:39.75,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:41.51,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.13,0:15:43.06,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.81,0:15:49.71,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.73,0:15:50.04,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Comment: 0,0:15:50.04,0:15:52.13,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,check timing of above two#
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.13,0:15:52.78,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.48,0:15:54.32,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.78,0:15:56.45,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're okay with the time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.88,0:15:58.73,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'll make sure I won't be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:01.05,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.71,0:16:01.96,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:06.80,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye.
Comment: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:11.99,Working - TS,,0000,0000,0000,,[Takanashi]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:14.40,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:17.01,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll be out for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.85,0:16:19.11,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll prepare lunch before I leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.48,0:16:20.90,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.56,0:16:22.86,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.35,0:16:23.96,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:25.50,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.56,0:16:28.64,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where Inami-san wants to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:29.61,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:31.90,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going somewhere with Inami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:32.64,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.66,0:16:34.78,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's been a lot going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.79,0:16:37.53,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, I want to see the result of all our hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.75,0:16:38.46,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Result?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.99,0:16:39.28,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.86,0:16:41.34,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,Result must mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.22,0:16:45.52,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}Does Onii-chan... like getting hit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:48.61,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}It's true.
Comment: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:49.50,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,check 2x fades
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:50.43,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.98,0:16:56.42,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What's wrong, Nazuna?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.81,0:16:58.41,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:16:59.01,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:00.58,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:06.24,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I wear tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:11.00,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially since tomorrow might become a really important day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:15.83,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:18.08,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I wear tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.24,0:17:19.75,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I bring?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.96,0:17:23.30,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my first time on a date, so I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:25.58,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which hairpin should I wear tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.01,0:17:27.72,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the ones I got from Takanashi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:29.77,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or the one he complimented for the first time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.03,0:17:31.51,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that would be too obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.99,0:17:32.31,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:35.23,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, we haven't even decided where to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:37.67,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look for something at the bookstore and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.75,0:17:39.77,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's closed already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:43.58,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, the person at the register is a guy, so even if it was open, I couldn't buy anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.81,0:17:46.63,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to find some reference material from something in my room.
