Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.26,0:18:08.83,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then Shinji hugged Yayoi tightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:12.81,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:14.46,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,Inami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.26,0:18:18.35,Working - Internal,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hug you tightly with these hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.15,0:18:22.15,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mahiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.82,0:18:23.21,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.85,0:18:25.88,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.40,0:18:28.69,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I heard a lot of noise from your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:31.20,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing with all these clothes out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.61,0:18:34.23,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know what to wear tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.86,0:18:36.10,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.05,0:18:39.73,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're cute no matter what you wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.35,0:18:41.69,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.57,0:18:48.61,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I got really confused when I was trying to\Nfigure out which hairpin to wear and where to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.75,0:18:51.67,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I really... don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:54.68,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you're having a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:56.80,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'm really worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:18:59.90,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost as if you're going on your first date.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:05.11,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You really like Takanashi-san, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.61,0:19:12.40,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to sleep now. You don't want to be tired all day tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.06,0:19:14.26,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.89,0:19:19.01,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.36,0:19:20.36,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.44,0:19:29.91,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Nothing has been solved yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.18,0:19:31.74,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not the clothes for tomorrow, nor where to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:33.90,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.47,0:19:36.31,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This?
