Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.93,0:19:43.83,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we'll have a clear day tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.98,0:19:56.46,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:19:58.99,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow...
