Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.08,0:23:15.18,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Katanashi-kun, are you all ready for tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.16,0:23:16.68,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I should be perfectly ready for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.73,0:23:18.31,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you dress up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.34,0:23:21.07,Working - Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Especially since they might end up being my burial clothes.
